text: Lara Hoffmann (born 25 March 1991) is a German sprinter. She competed in the 4 x 400 metres relay at the 2016 Summer Olympics. The team finished 5th in their heat and did not advance to the final. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:German athletics biography stubs Category:German female sprinters Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic athletes of Germany
